source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_DEFAULT_TALK_1<tab>Greetings! I take it you have come to see me about a retainer.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_DEFAULT_TALK_1<tab><var 08 E3E90C0D ((<var 08 E3E90C05 ((Bonsoir)) ((Bonjour)) /var>)) ((<var 08 E3E90C12 ((Bonjour)) ((Bonsoir)) /var>)) /var><var 1D /var>! En quoi puis-je vous aider<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_DEFAULT_TALK_2<tab>Retainers are hardworking lads and lasses who will help you to manage those spoils earned while off slaying dragons or whatever it is you adventurers do.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_DEFAULT_TALK_2<tab>... Ah, mais je vois que vous débutez dans le métier d'aventurier. J'imagine donc que vous ignorez ce que je fais là, et plus précisément à quoi sert ce comptoir.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_DEFAULT_TALK_3<tab>Unfortunately, you do not appear you could even slay an eft, let alone a dragon, therefore I must decline any petition you may have to take a retainer into your employ.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_DEFAULT_TALK_3<tab>Pour faire simple, je m'occupe de tout ce qui a trait aux servants. C'est donc ici que vous devrez vous présenter quand vous voudrez en recruter un.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_DEFAULT_TALK_4<tab>Build yourself a reputation in this city, however, and I shall provide you with whatever it is you need. Might I suggest you start by heading back to the Adventurers' Guild and seeing if someone there has work for you?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_DEFAULT_TALK_4<tab>Mais pour obtenir ce privilège, il va d'abord falloir faire vos preuves sur le terrain. Si vous montrez que vous êtes disposé<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> à aider les autres, alors la guilde vous fera bénéficier de multiples avantages, à commencer par le service d'embauche de servants. En espérant vous revoir bientôt<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_EXPLANATION_MENU_WHAT_IS<tab>Who are retainers?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_EXPLANATION_MENU_WHAT_IS<tab>Le rôle des servants

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_EXPLANATION_MENU_ABOUT<tab>What services can retainers provide?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_EXPLANATION_MENU_ABOUT<tab>Les services proposés par les servants

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_EXPLANATION_MENU_CALL<tab>How do I summon a retainer?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_EXPLANATION_MENU_CALL<tab>La façon d'appeler ses servants

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_MAIN_MENU_BACK<tab>Nothing
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_MAIN_MENU_BACK<tab>Retour

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ABOUT_TALK_01<tab>Retainers are men and women who offer their services in exchange for coin. Though they're seldom as sharp as adventurers like yourself, they're no strangers to life's more menial tasks─tasks which your lot might not think worth your time.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ABOUT_TALK_01<tab>Les servants sont des personnes qui aident les aventuriers en s'occupant de certaines tâches fastidieuses, comme par exemple la vente d'objets ou la gestion d'inventaire.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ABOUT_TALK_02<tab>Retainers can provide a host of different services, from tending your items to protecting your gil. Oh, and you need not worry about providing recompense for a retainer's services, for the Adventurers' Guild will not only cover his salary, but also replace anything that goes missing, should you wake up to find your belongings gone and your retainer nowhere to be found.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ABOUT_TALK_02<tab>Leurs gages sont entièrement pris en charge par la guilde des aventuriers, autrement dit leurs services ne vous coûteront pas un gil.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ITEMS_GIL_TALK_01<tab>Another job retainers are often asked to perform is the tending of items placed up for sale in the markets─something many adventurers cannot be bothered to do themselves.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ITEMS_GIL_TALK_01<tab>Les servants peuvent vous aider à gérer votre inventaire en gardant le matériel qui vous encombre. Ils peuvent aussi s'occuper de vendre des objets pour vous sur les marchés.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ITEMS_GIL_TALK_02<tab>If you wish to experience the market for yourself, I ask that you seek out one of the nearby boards.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ITEMS_GIL_TALK_02<tab>Sachez enfin qu'il est possible de les envoyer en mission afin qu'ils chassent des créatures ou recherchent des matériaux pour vous. Il y a certaines conditions à l'exécution de ces tâches, mais cela fait partie de leurs qualifications.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CALL_TALK_01<tab>Retainers in your employ can be summoned at any time using special bells like the one nearby.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CALL_TALK_01<tab>Vous pouvez les appeler au moyen de sonnettes spéciales, comme celle qui se trouve à votre gauche.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CALL_TALK_02<tab>Summoning bells can also be found around the realm in oft-visited locations such as city markets and inns.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CALL_TALK_02<tab>Il y en a généralement près des tableaux des ventes, mais vous en trouverez également dans tous les autres lieux de passage, à savoir les auberges, les hameaux, les centres de divertissement... Bref, un peu partout<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CASHBACK_ASK_ABOUT<tab>Learn about Market Tax
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CASHBACK_ASK_ABOUT<tab>Savoir à quoi servent les réductions de taxe

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CASHBACK_EXPLANATION<tab>To make their markets more attractive to prospective sellers, cities will often lower the percentage of tax that is collected from each sale.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CASHBACK_EXPLANATION<tab>Il arrive souvent que les cités réduisent la taxe qu'elles prélèvent sur les ventes afin de favoriser l'activité de leur marché.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CASHBACK_CAUTION<tab>Reduced tax rate periods can end earlier than indicated if areas require maintenance.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CASHBACK_CAUTION<tab>Les périodes de réduction peuvent être plus courtes qu'annoncées si une maintenance est nécessaire dans la zone concernée.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CREATE_TALK_01<tab>According to our records, you may hire up to <var 20 E802 /var> retainers.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CREATE_TALK_01<tab>D'après le registre, vous pouvez employer <var 20 E802 /var> servant<var 08 E2E80202 (()) ((s)) /var> au maximum.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_NO_RETAINERS_TALK<tab>Currently, you have no retainers in your employ.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_NO_RETAINERS_TALK<tab>Je vois que vous n'en avez ac<var 16 /var>tu<var 16 /var>el<var 16 /var>le<var 16 /var>ment aucun à votre service.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_HAVE_RETAINERS_TALK<tab>Currently, you have <var 20 E802 /var> <var 08 E4E80202 ((retainer)) ((retainers)) /var> in your employ.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_HAVE_RETAINERS_TALK<tab>Je vois que vous en avez ac<var 16 /var>tu<var 16 /var>el<var 16 /var>le<var 16 /var>ment <var 20 E802 /var> à votre service.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CUSTOMIZE_WARNING<tab>While customizing your retainer, you will be unable to communicate with players and engage in other activities.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CUSTOMIZE_WARNING<tab>Vous serez incapable de communiquer avec les autres joueurs ou d'effectuer d'autres actions durant ce processus.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CUSTOMIZE_TALK<tab>Excellent. We have quite a few men and women on our lists, so I invite you to describe the retainer you desire, down to the most minute detail.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CUSTOMIZE_TALK<tab>Nous avons de nombreuses personnes inscrites dans nos registres. Je vous invite donc à choisir le type de servant qui vous conviendrait le mieux.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_DUTY_FINDER_WARNING<tab>Beginning the retainer customization process will automatically cancel your Duty Finder registration.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_DUTY_FINDER_WARNING<tab>Le processus d'embauche d'un servant annule au<var 16 /var>to<var 16 /var>ma<var 16 /var>ti<var 16 /var>que<var 16 /var>ment tout enregistrement dans l'outil de mission.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_DUTY_FINDER_CONFIRM<tab>Withdraw duty registration and hire a retainer?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_DUTY_FINDER_CONFIRM<tab>Poursuivre le processus d'embauche<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_TALK<tab>I can think of several retainers that are exactly as you describe. Oddly enough, they have strikingly different personalities. If you would be so kind as to state a preference, it would be most helpful.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_TALK<tab>J'ai plusieurs candidats qui correspondent à vos souhaits. Est-ce que vous avez une préférence pour ce qui est de la personnalité<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_TITLE<tab>Select your retainer's personality.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_TITLE<tab>Choisissez la personnalité du servant

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_CHEERFUL<tab>Polite.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_CHEERFUL<tab>Poli

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_WILD<tab>Rough.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_WILD<tab>Brusque

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_COOLHEADED<tab>Serious.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_COOLHEADED<tab>Sérieux

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_CAREFREE<tab>Carefree.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_CAREFREE<tab>Insouciant

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_PROBLEMATIC<tab>Independent.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_PROBLEMATIC<tab>Indépendant

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_PLAYFUL<tab>Lively.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_PLAYFUL<tab>Enjoué

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CHECK_PERSONALITY_ENTER<tab>Very well, I have just the individual in mind. When summoned, this retainer will greet you just so:
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CHECK_PERSONALITY_ENTER<tab>Je crois avoir quelqu'un qui vous donnera entière sa<var 16 /var>tis<var 16 /var>fac<var 16 /var>tion. Lorsque vous l'appellerez, ce servant vous saluera comme ça...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CHECK_PERSONALITY_LEAVE<tab>And when dismissed, this retainer will bid you farewell just so:
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CHECK_PERSONALITY_LEAVE<tab>Et lorsque vous vous séparerez, ce servant vous dira ceci...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CHECK_PERSONALITY_CONFIRM<tab>Hire this retainer?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CHECK_PERSONALITY_CONFIRM<tab>Choisir ce caractère pour le servant<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_NAME_ASK<tab>Excellent. It is also customary to give a retainer an appellation of one's own making─a nickname, as it were. We find this deepens the bond between our clients and their retainers.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_NAME_ASK<tab>Il est de coutume chez nous de choisir un surnom par lequel on appelle son servant. Cela permet de renforcer le lien qui unit nos clients à leurs employés.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_NAME_PROMPT_TITLE<tab>Retainer Nickname
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_NAME_PROMPT_TITLE<tab>Surnom du servant

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_NAME_PROMPT_MESSAGE0<tab>Give your retainer a nickname.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_NAME_PROMPT_MESSAGE0<tab>Donnez un surnom à votre servant

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_NAME_PROMPT_MESSAGE1<tab>Names must be at least 3 characters long and can contain letters, apostrophes, and hyphens. Please note, however, that hyphens cannot be used in succession or placed immediately before or after apostrophes.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_NAME_PROMPT_MESSAGE1Les lettres de l'alphabet latin standard ainsi que l'apostrophe et le tiret peuvent être utilisés.
Le tiret ne peut pas être employé plusieurs fois à la suite, ni en combinaison avec l'apostrophe.
Le surnom doit commencer par une lettre et faire au moins trois caractères.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_NAME_PROMPT_HEAD<tab>
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_NAME_PROMPT_HEAD<tab>Surnom du servant

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CANCEL_CONFIRM<tab>Are you certain you wish to cancel the hiring process?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CANCEL_CONFIRM<tab>Êtes-vous sûr<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> de vouloir annuler le processus d'embauche<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CREATE_CONFIRM<tab>Hire the services of <var 29 EA02 /var>?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CREATE_CONFIRM<tab>Confirmer l'embauche de <var 29 EA02 /var><var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_CREATE<tab>Hire a retainer?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_CREATE<tab>Voulez-vous engager un nouveau servant<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_CREATE_YES<tab>Yes
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_CREATE_YES<tab>Oui

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_CREATE_NO<tab>No
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_CREATE_NO<tab>Non

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CREATING_RETAINER<tab>One moment, please, while I draft the proper documentation.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CREATING_RETAINER<tab>Bien, je vais consigner tout ça dans le registre.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CREATE_SUCCESS_01<tab>Congratulations! <var 2B ((<var 29 EA02 /var>)) /var> is now in your employ.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CREATE_SUCCESS_01<tab>... Voilà qui est fait. Les formalités d'embauche de <var 29 EA02 /var> sont à présent terminées.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CREATE_SUCCESS_02<tab>You can summon your new retainer using the nearby bell.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CREATE_SUCCESS_02<tab>Vous pouvez l'appeler quand bon vous semble à l'aide des sonnettes spéciales, comme celle qui se trouve sur votre gauche. Celles-ci sont généralement disposées près des tableaux de vente.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CREATE_SUCCESS_03<tab>If you have any further questions or requests, please do not hesitate to ask.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CREATE_SUCCESS_03<tab>Essayez donc et confiez-lui quelques affaires pour commencer.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_CREATE_FAILED_NAME<tab>The name you have chosen is not available. Please select another.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_CREATE_FAILED_NAME<tab>Le surnom que vous avez choisi ne peut pas être donné à votre servant. Veuillez en choisir un autre.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_CREATE_FULL<tab>I am sorry, but you cannot hire any more retainers.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_CREATE_FULL<tab>Je suis désolée, mais vous avez déjà atteint le nombre maximum de servants autorisé...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_CREATE_CANCEL<tab>Understood. If you change your mind, speak with me again.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_CREATE_CANCEL<tab>Comme vous voulez. N'hésitez pas à revenir me voir si vous changez d'avis.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REGISTER_TALK_LIMSA_01<tab>Select the retainer you wish to send to the markets in Limsa Lominsa.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REGISTER_TALK_LIMSA_01<tab>Choisissez le servant que vous désirez transférer au marché de Limsa Lominsa.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REGISTER_ASK_LIMSA<tab>Send <var 2B ((<var 29 EA02 /var>)) /var> to Limsa Lominsa?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REGISTER_ASK_LIMSA<tab>Transférer <var 29 EA02 /var> à Limsa Lominsa<var 1D /var>?

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REGISTER_SUCCESS_LIMSA<tab>Le servant “<var 29 EA02 /var>” est désormais inscrit au marché de Limsa Lominsa.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REGISTER_ALREADY_LIMSA<tab>That retainer is already in Limsa Lominsa.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REGISTER_ALREADY_LIMSA<tab>Ce servant est déjà inscrit au marché de Limsa Lominsa.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REGISTER_TALK_OLDSHARLAYAN_01<tab>Select the retainer you wish to send to the markets in Old Sharlayan.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REGISTER_TALK_OLDSHARLAYAN_01<tab>Choisissez le servant que vous désirez transférer au marché de Vieille Sharlayan.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REGISTER_ASK_YES<tab>Yes
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REGISTER_ASK_YES<tab>Oui

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REGISTER_ASK_NO<tab>No
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REGISTER_ASK_NO<tab>Non

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REMAKE_RETAINER_EXPLANATION<tab>You...are dissatisfied with one of your retainers? Very well. If you would be so kind as to inform me which retainer is lacking, we can begin the review process.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REMAKE_RETAINER_EXPLANATIONVous souhaitez modifier quelques aspects de vos servants? Très bien.
Laissez-moi d'abord vérifier dans mon registre.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REMAKE_RETAINER_TALK<tab>You may change your retainers' nicknames or instruct them to visit the aesthetician at any time. If you desire more drastic changes to a retainer's appearance or personality, the retainer vocate will assist you in finding a replacement of comparable skill and experience.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REMAKE_RETAINER_TALK<tab>Quel servant désirez-vous remodeler<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_REMAKE<tab>Review your specifications for <var 2B ((<var 29 EA02 /var>)) /var>?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_REMAKE<tab>Remodeler “<var 29 EA02 /var>”<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_REMAKE_YES<tab>Yes
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_REMAKE_YES<tab>Oui

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_REMAKE_NO<tab>No
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_REMAKE_NO<tab>Non

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_REMAKE_CANCEL<tab>Then you <var 1A 02 /var>are<var 1A 01 /var> completely satisfied with your retainer? Understood. Pray speak with me again should your preferences change.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_REMAKE_CANCEL<tab>Je suis au regret de vous dire que la demande de remodelage de votre servant a été interrompue. Si vous désirez la reprendre, adressez-vous à moi.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_DUTY_FINDER_CONFIRM_REMAKE<tab>Withdraw duty registration and review your retainer?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_DUTY_FINDER_CONFIRM_REMAKE<tab>Poursuivre le remodelage du servant<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_REMAKE_TALK<tab>Very well. First, let us review your retainer's current appearance. I must ask that you describe in detail which aspects you find unappealing, and what you would prefer.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_REMAKE_TALK<tab>Veuillez commencer par me décrire l'apparence que vous recherchez.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_TALK_REMAKE<tab>I see... Next, I would have you confirm your preference with regards to personality. “The right retainer for the right person,” as we are wont to say.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_PERSONALITY_TALK_REMAKE<tab>J'en prends note. Passons maintenant au caractère.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CHECK_PERSONALITY_REMAKE_ENTER<tab>To ensure there is no misunderstanding, know that your retainer will address you just so:
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CHECK_PERSONALITY_REMAKE_ENTER<tab>Avec ce type de personnalité, le servant vous saluera comme ceci...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CHECK_PERSONALITY_CONFIRM_REMAKE<tab>Are you satisfied with this personality?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CHECK_PERSONALITY_CONFIRM_REMAKE<tab>Choisir ce caractère pour le servant<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_NAME_ASK_REMAKE<tab>Understood. Finally, I must needs verify the nickname you would give your retainer. You may register the same nickname if you like.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_NAME_ASK_REMAKEVoilà une autre chose de faite. Avez-vous une idée pour son surnom?
Bien sûr, rien ne vous oblige de le changer.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CANCEL_CONFIRM_REMAKE<tab>Are you certain you wish to cancel the review process?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CANCEL_CONFIRM_REMAKE<tab>Terminer le remodelage du servant<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REMAKE_CONFIRM<tab>Complete your review of <var 29 EA02 /var>?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REMAKE_CONFIRM<tab>Confirmer le remodelage de “<var 29 EA02 /var>”<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REMEKE_RETAINER<tab>One moment, please, while I draft the proper documentation.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REMEKE_RETAINER<tab>Parfait<var 1D /var>! Nous allons effectuer le remodelage de votre servant. Veuillez patienter un instant, s'il vous plaît.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_EQUIP_HAVE_RETAINER<tab>Forgive me, but you must first instruct your retainer to remove all equipment. A necessary precaution, in light of past incidents.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_EQUIP_HAVE_RETAINER<tab>Le remodelage ne peut pas être opéré si votre servant porte d'autres pièces d'équipement qu'une arme/outil principal. Vous devez d'abord les retirer.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_VENTURE_RETAINER<tab>Our records indicate that your retainer is currently undertaking a venture. Until that is no longer the case, I fear we cannot begin the review process.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_VENTURE_RETAINER<tab>Le remodelage ne peut pas être opéré si votre servant est en train d'effectuer une tâche. Veuillez attendre qu'il ait fini ce qu'il est en train de faire.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_REMAKE_FAILED<tab>Due to unforeseen circumstances, we cannot review your retainer at this time.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_REMAKE_FAILED<tab>Le remodelage du servant a échoué.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REMAKE_SUCCESS_01<tab>I am pleased to inform you that your review has been processed, and <var 29 EA02 /var> is now ready to serve you.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REMAKE_SUCCESS_01<tab>Le remodelage de “<var 29 EA02 /var>” est terminé.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REMAKE_SUCCESS_02<tab>You can summon your retainer using the nearby bell.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REMAKE_SUCCESS_02<tab>Appelez votre servant avec une sonnette pour constater le résultat.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REMOVE_RETAINER_EXPLANATION<tab>Very well. Allow me a moment to locate your documentation.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REMOVE_RETAINER_EXPLANATION<tab>Vous voulez congédier définitivement un servant<var 1D /var>? Laissez-moi d'abord vérifier vos in<var 16 /var>for<var 16 /var>ma<var 16 /var>tions dans le registre...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_NO_RETAINERS_AVAILABLE<tab>It does not appear you have any retainers in your employ at this time.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_NO_RETAINERS_AVAILABLE<tab>Je regrette, mais vous n'avez ac<var 16 /var>tu<var 16 /var>el<var 16 /var>le<var 16 /var>ment aucun servant à votre service...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REMOVE_RETAINER_TALK<tab>Confirm the retainer you wish to release.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_REMOVE_RETAINER_TALK<tab>Quel servant voulez-vous congédier<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_REMOVE<tab>Release <var 2B ((<var 29 EA02 /var>)) /var>?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_REMOVE<tab>Renvoyer définitivement <var 29 EA02 /var><var 1D /var>?

source:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_REMOVE_HASHOUSERelease )) /var>?
Please be advised that retainers placed in estates will not be automatically removed.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_REMOVE_HASHOUSERenvoyer définitivement ?
Notez que si ce servant est affecté dans un logement au moment de l'opération, il restera visible sur le terrain même après avoir été congédié.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_REMOVE_YES<tab>Yes
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_REMOVE_YES<tab>Oui

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_REMOVE_NO<tab>No
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_REMOVE_NO<tab>Non

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_REMOVE_SUCCESS<tab><var 2B ((<var 29 EA02 /var>)) /var> is released from service.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_REMOVE_SUCCESS<tab>Vous avez congédié <var 29 EA02 /var>...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_REMOVE_FAILED_INVENTORY<tab>Our records show that the retainer you wish to release is still in possession of several of your belongings. You must retrieve those belongings before I can approve the dismissal.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_REMOVE_FAILED_INVENTORY<tab>Votre servant a ac<var 16 /var>tu<var 16 /var>el<var 16 /var>le<var 16 /var>ment des objets ou gils en sa possession. Vous devez d'abord récupérer tout ce que vous lui avez confié avant de pouvoir le renvoyer.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_REMOVE_CANCEL<tab>Understood. The retainer shall remain in your employ. Speak with me again if you change your mind.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RETAINER_REMOVE_CANCEL<tab>Vous avez changé d'avis<var 1D /var>? Très bien. N'hésitez pas à revenir, si besoin.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_JOB_MENU_TITLE<tab>What would you like to do?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_JOB_MENU_TITLE<tab>Que voulez-vous faire<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_JOB_MENU_HOWTO<tab>Ask about assigning your retainer a job.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_JOB_MENU_HOWTO<tab>Savoir comment attribuer un job à un servant

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_JOB_MENU_RELATION<tab>Ask about job requirements.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_JOB_MENU_RELATION<tab>Connaître la relation entre classe et job

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_JOB_MENU_OBTAIN<tab>Purchase a copy of <var 1A 02 /var>Modern Vocation<var 1A 01 /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_JOB_MENU_OBTAIN<tab>Acheter <var 33 ((Item)) 02E8020202 /var>

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_JOB_MENU_CANCEL<tab>Nothing.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_JOB_MENU_CANCEL<tab>Retour

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_JOB_HOWTO_TALK_01<tab>By popular demand, we have prepared an exhaustive publication to aid clients who would have their retainers train in certain ancient or esoteric traditions.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_JOB_HOWTO_TALK_01<tab>Si vous faites partie de ces gens qui redonnent vie aux disciplines de combat et de magie ancestrales, vous pouvez noter vos con<var 16 /var>nais<var 16 /var>san<var 16 /var>ces et vos expériences dans <var 33 ((Item)) 02E8020202 /var> pour les transmettre à un servant.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_JOB_HOWTO_TALK_02<tab>To assign your retainer a <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>job<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>, you must first obtain <var 31 ((Item)) 02E8020202 /var>, which can be purchased from the retainer vocate for 40 ventures.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_JOB_HOWTO_TALK_02<tab>Pour attribuer un job à un servant, il est nécessaire d'acquérir <var 33 ((Item)) 02E8020202 /var> en échange de 40 jetons de tâche.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_JOB_HOWTO_TALK_03<tab>Furthermore, you must have achieved level 50 in the job you wish to assign your retainer. Please note that the jobs you can assign your retainer are determined by their class. Limited jobs are not available.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_JOB_HOWTO_TALK_03<tab>Cependant, il est impossible de transmettre les con<var 16 /var>nais<var 16 /var>san<var 16 /var>ces d'un job restreint ou celles d'un job avec lequel on n'a pas atteint le niveau 50.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_JOB_HOWTO_TALK_04<tab>If you wish to assign a level 50 retainer a job which is not currently available, you will need to reset and change their class.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_JOB_HOWTO_TALK_04<tab>Une fois qu'un job a été attribué à un servant, il est nécessaire de le réinitialiser avant de pouvoir lui choisir un autre job ou classe.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RELATION_TALK_01<tab>As you may know, a certain measure of experience is required before a retainer may train in a more advanced tradition.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RELATION_TALK_01<tab>Pour pouvoir transmettre les con<var 16 /var>nais<var 16 /var>san<var 16 /var>ces d'une discipline de combat ou de magie ancestrale à un servant, il faut bien sûr que celui-ci et vous-même ayez la maîtrise de certaines compétences. Mais cela, vous l'avez sûrement déjà appris par la pratique.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RELATION_MENU_TITLE<tab>Select a class.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RELATION_MENU_TITLE<tab>Quelle est la classe du servant<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RELATION_MENU_CLASS<tab><var 2B ((<var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80201 /var>)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RELATION_MENU_CLASS<tab><var 2B ((<var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80201 /var>)) /var>

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RELATION_MENU_CANCEL<tab>Return.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_RELATION_MENU_CANCEL<tab>Retour

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CONDITIONS_TALK_01<tab>A retainer who has been assigned the <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80201 /var> class may be eligible to train in the following traditions:
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CONDITIONS_TALK_01<tab>Un servant dont la classe est <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80201 /var> pourra apprendre l'un des jobs de la liste qui suit.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CONDITIONS_MENU_TITLE<tab>Select a job.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CONDITIONS_MENU_TITLE<tab>Quel job désirez-vous attribuer<var 1D /var>?

Additionally, your retainer must have achieved level 30 as <var 08 E4E8030B ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80301 /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E8030F ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80301 /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E80306 ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80301 /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E8031B ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80301 /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E80322 ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80301 /var>)) ((a <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80301 /var>)) /var>)) /var>)) /var>)) /var>)) /var>.

De son côté, le servant doit être <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80301 /var> de niveau 30 ou plus.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CONDITIONS_TALK_20<tab>To assign your retainer the <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80201 /var> job, you yourself must first achieve level 50 as <var 08 E4E8020B ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80201 /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E8020F ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80201 /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E80206 ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80201 /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E8021B ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80201 /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E80222 ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80201 /var>)) ((a <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80201 /var>)) /var>)) /var>)) /var>)) /var>)) /var>. Additionally, your retainer must have achieved level 50 as a Disciple of War or Magic.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CONDITIONS_TALK_20<tab>Pour transmettre vos con<var 16 /var>nais<var 16 /var>san<var 16 /var>ces du job “<var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80201 /var>”, vous devez vous-même avoir atteint au moins le niveau 50 avec. De son côté, le servant doit être de niveau 50 ou plus dans une classe de disciple de la guerre ou de la magie.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CONDITIONS_TALK_30<tab>To assign your retainer the <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80201 /var> job, you yourself must first achieve level 60 as <var 08 E4E8020B ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80201 /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E8020F ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80201 /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E80206 ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80201 /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E8021B ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80201 /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E80222 ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80201 /var>)) ((a <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80201 /var>)) /var>)) /var>)) /var>)) /var>)) /var>. target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CONDITIONS_TALK_30<tab>Pour transmettre vos con<var 16 /var>nais<var 16 /var>san<var 16 /var>ces du job “<var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80201 /var>”, vous devez vous-même avoir atteint au moins le niveau 60 avec. De son côté, le servant doit être de niveau 60 ou plus dans une classe de disciple de la guerre ou de la magie.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CONDITIONS_TALK_40<tab>To assign your retainer the <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80201 /var> job, you yourself must first achieve level 70 as <var 08 E4E8020B ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80201 /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E8020F ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80201 /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E80206 ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80201 /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E8021B ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80201 /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E80222 ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80201 /var>)) ((a <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80201 /var>)) /var>)) /var>)) /var>)) /var>)) /var>. target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_CONDITIONS_TALK_40<tab>Pour transmettre vos con<var 16 /var>nais<var 16 /var>san<var 16 /var>ces du job “<var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80201 /var>”, vous devez vous-même avoir atteint au moins le niveau 70 avec. De son côté, le servant doit être de niveau 70 ou plus dans une classe de disciple de la guerre ou de la magie.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_SCROLL_HAS_ALREADY<tab>Ahem. If I am not mistaken, do you not already have a copy of that publication in your possession?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_SCROLL_HAS_ALREADY<tab>Mais que dites-vous<var 1D /var>? D'après nos registres, vous avez déjà <var 33 ((Item)) 02E8020202 /var> et vous ne l'avez pas remis à un de nos employés...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_SCROLL_TALK_01<tab>You already possess a copy of <var 1A 02 /var>Modern Vocation<var 1A 01 /var>. You may summon a retainer and assign them a job, if they meet the necessary requirements.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_SCROLL_TALK_01<tab>Vous pouvez désormais utiliser l'option “Attribuer un job du servant” lorsque vous en appelez un avec une sonnette.

target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_SCROLL_TRADE<tab>Acheter <var 33 ((Item)) 02E8020202 /var> en échange de 40 jetons de tâche<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERDESK_00009_ASK_SCROLL_YES<tab>Yes
